Compatible with LZAP 3.10.0

These macros aim to develop the S2 and SS-MS scatter selection criteria for both high for MDC2 data.

The data files used are listed in the .list files. The corresponding plots are contained in the .root files by the same name.

Steps to run:
./configure.py --force /path/sampleDataFile.root (only have to do once)
./macro.py MyProcessor.C fileList.list (for optional arguements, ./macro.py -h)

Results of this study can be found here: https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1j8KF4adJYf8x3l3kR4a-q_7m-aenNK8_v7x7xoBM_p8/edit?usp=sharing